  "detailed_description": "<strong>Sokosignal</strong> is a puzzle game in which you send a signal with each move you make. Some objects will receive your signal and attempt to copy your move, others will not. Some will resend your signal, others will both resend and attempt to copy. Place the right objects on the marked spots to solve each puzzle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/b514565ac7553883535b592cea28bbb0.poster.avif?t=1763508124\" width=296 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/b514565ac7553883535b592cea28bbb0.webm?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/b514565ac7553883535b592cea28bbb0.mp4?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/a1af7f714b84f58f4c6d5e0f94bc520c.poster.avif?t=1763508124\" width=294 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/a1af7f714b84f58f4c6d5e0f94bc520c.webm?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/a1af7f714b84f58f4c6d5e0f94bc520c.mp4?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>unique action at a distance mechanic</li><li>six parts, each adding new objects with new properties</li><li>over 80 handcrafted levels</li><li>unlimited undo</li><li>no tutorial and minimal text - levels designed to teach you new mechanics by doing</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Sokosignal</strong> is a puzzle game in which you send a signal with each move you make. Some objects will receive your signal and attempt to copy your move, others will not. Some will resend your signal, others will both resend and attempt to copy. Place the right objects on the marked spots to solve each puzzle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/b514565ac7553883535b592cea28bbb0.poster.avif?t=1763508124\" width=296 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/b514565ac7553883535b592cea28bbb0.webm?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/b514565ac7553883535b592cea28bbb0.mp4?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/a1af7f714b84f58f4c6d5e0f94bc520c.poster.avif?t=1763508124\" width=294 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/a1af7f714b84f58f4c6d5e0f94bc520c.webm?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154700/extras/a1af7f714b84f58f4c6d5e0f94bc520c.mp4?t=1763508124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>unique action at a distance mechanic</li><li>six parts, each adding new objects with new properties</li><li>over 80 handcrafted levels</li><li>unlimited undo</li><li>no tutorial and minimal text - levels designed to teach you new mechanics by doing</li></ul>",
